== GNOME to Launchpad ==

This is a list mapping gnome modules from damned lies to the locations that they can be translated in launchpad. This way teams can keep those translations in sync.

=== GNOME - 2.26 ===

Those are the GNOME modules, ordered as they appear in the <nowiki>[[http://l10n.gnome.org/releases/gnome-2-26/|GNOME 2.26 (UI) module set]]</nowiki> page.
